cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM 

This paper focuses on generating realistic images from text descriptions, which is a task related to computer vision (CV). Therefore, cs.CV is the most likely sub-category. The proposed method also involves the use of a dynamic memory module and a response gate, which are components of deep learning models (LG). Additionally, the method utilizes text information to generate images, which is a task related to natural language processing (NLP) and artificial intelligence (AI). Therefore, cs.AI and cs.CL are also likely sub-categories. Finally, the paper evaluates the proposed method on two datasets, which is a task related to multimedia (MM). Therefore, cs.MM is also a likely sub-category.
